        <tags>cvss_base_vector=CVSS:3.1/AV:N/AC:H/PR:N/UI:N/S:C/C:H/I:H/A:H|summary=Apache HTTP Server is prone to multiple vulnerabilities.|insight=The following vulnerabilities exist:

