  unauthenticated to conduct MITM attacks on internal server subrequests or direct the server to
  initiate connections to arbitrary hosts or to cause a denial of service.|solution=Update to version 5.6.24, 7.0.9 or later.|vuldetect=Checks if a vulnerable version is present on the target host.|solution_type=VendorFix</tags>
