  - IBM solidDB

  - Oracle Database

  - Microsoft SQL Server|impact=Successful exploitation could allow an attacker to obtain
  sensitive information from the database.|solution=Restrict database access to remote systems. Please see the
  manual of the affected database server for more information.|vuldetect=Checks the result of various database server detections and
  evaluates their results.|solution_type=Workaround</tags>
